📦 Python Libraries (Concept)
What Are Libraries?
Libraries = Prebuilt collections of functions to avoid writing everything from scratch.
Key Libraries We'll Use:
Library	Use
pandas	Tabular data (like Excel)
numpy	Arrays and numerical operations
matplotlib	Data visualization
yfinance	Pull stock data from Yahoo Finance
scipy.optimize	For portfolio optimization
sqlite3	Save data to a local SQL database
plotly / Power BI	Optional for interactive dashboards
